  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What are Resource Hints?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Resource hints are directives that help the browser decide which resources to load earlier or prepare in advance."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Why Resource Hints Matter"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "They reduce latency and improve page load speed by optimizing how and when resources are fetched."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Types of Resource Hints"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "value": {
        "headers": ["Hint", "Purpose"],
        "rows": [
          ["preload", "Load critical resources immediately"],
          ["prefetch", "Load resources for future navigation"],
          ["preconnect", "Establish early connection to server"],
          ["dns-prefetch", "Resolve DNS early"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Preload Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"preload\" href=\"style.css\" as=\"style\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Prefetch Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"prefetch\" href=\"next-page.html\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Preconnect Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://example.com\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "DNS Prefetch Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"//example.com\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use preload only for critical resources**",
        "**Use prefetch for next-page assets**",
        "**Use preconnect for external domains**",
        "**Avoid excessive resource hints**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Overusing preload causing network congestion**",
        "**Using prefetch for critical resources**",
        "**Ignoring priority levels**",
        "**Not testing performance impact**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Resource hints help browsers load resources smarter and faster. When used correctly, they significantly improve performance and user experience."
    }
